  <section id="Section518778">
    <title><anchor id="Anchor548932" role="Index"
    xreflabel="sales representatives:master list of" /> <indexterm
        significance="normal" zone="Anchor548932">
        <primary>sales representatives</primary>

        <secondary>master list of</secondary>
      </indexterm>Sales Representatives</title>

    <para id="Para518779">To access the master list of Sales Representatives,
    select the "Sales Reps" option. The following screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para518783"><screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="images/SO_MI_salesRepList.png"
                       id="Graphic522970" />
          </imageobject>

          <caption id="Caption518784">Sales Representatives Master
          List</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot></para>

    <para id="Para518785">The Sales Representatives master list displays the
    name, identification number, and active status of all existing Sales
    Representatives.</para>

    <para id="Para518786">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518787">CLOSE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1868f34">
          <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para653613">PRINT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1868f7c">
          <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518789">NEW</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1868fc4">
          <para>Opens screen for creating a new Sales Representative.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518790">EDIT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x186900c">
          <para>Enables you to edit highlighted Sales Representative. The edit
          screen is the same as that for creating a new Sales
          Representative--except that when editing, the fields will contain
          Sales Representative information. Double-clicking on a Sales
          Representative will also bring you to the editing screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518791">VIEW</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1869054">
          <para>Highlight a Sales Representative and then select this button
          to reach a read-only view of the "Edit" screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518792">DELETE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x186909c">
          <para>Highlight a Sales Representative and then select this button
          to remove the Sales Representative from the master list.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para522152">Right-clicking on a Sales Representative in the
    Sales Representatives master list enables you to select from the following
    menu options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518794">Edit Sales Rep</term>

        <xi:include href="../so.xml"
                    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                    xpointer="element(listitemN0x180ac00N0x186900c)" />
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518795">View Sales Rep</term>

        <xi:include href="../so.xml"
                    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                    xpointer="element(listitemN0x180ac00N0x1869054)" />
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518796">Delete Sales Rep</term>

        <xi:include href="../so.xml"
                    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                    xpointer="element(listitemN0x180ac00N0x186909c)" />
      </varlistentry>

      <xi:include href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml"
                  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                  xpointer="element(xtreewidget.menu.exportcontents)" />
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para518798"><anchor id="Anchor555570" role="Index"
    xreflabel="sales representatives:creating new" /> <indexterm
        significance="normal" zone="Anchor555570">
        <primary>sales representatives</primary>

        <secondary>creating new</secondary>
      </indexterm>To create a new Sales Representative, select the NEW button.
    The following screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para518802"><screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="images/SO_MI_salesRepNew.png"
                       id="Graphic522992" />
          </imageobject>

          <caption id="Caption518803">Create New Sales
          Representative</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot></para>

    <para id="Para518804">When creating a new Sales Representative, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518808">Number</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1869300">
          <para>Enter an identification number for the Sales
          Representative.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518810">Active</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1869348">
          <para>Select if the Sales Representative is currently active.</para>

          <para id="Para518811">Not selecting means the Sales Representative
          is inactive.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518815">Name</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1869390">
          <para>Enter the name of the Sales Representative.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518820"><anchor id="Anchor555572" role="Index"
        xreflabel="sales representatives:commission percentages for" />
        <indexterm significance="normal" zone="Anchor555572">
            <primary>sales representatives</primary>

            <secondary>commission percentages for</secondary>
          </indexterm>Comm. Prcnt</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1869420">
          <para>Enter the commission percentage for the Sales Representative.
          For example, if the commission is to be 5%, enter the value
          ".05".</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para518822">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518823">CANCEL</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x186948c">
          <para>Closes the screen without creating a Sales Representative,
          returning you to the application desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para518824">SAVE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18694d4">
          <para>Creates the Sales Representative and enters their information
          into the master list of Sales Representatives.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>